的网站被构建并作为静态文件（HTML、CSS、JS）进行服务，任何静态文件服务器都可以提供这些文件。",[231,235,236],{},"Nuxt Content 可以使用 Nuxt 预渲染部署到静态托管。",[226,238,240],{"id":239},"使用-ssg-构建","使用 SSG 构建",[231,242,243],{},"要使用静态站点生成构建您的应用，请运行以下命令：",[245,246,251],"pre",{"className":247,"code":248,"language":249,"meta":250,"style":250},"language-bash shiki shiki-themes material-theme-lighter material-theme material-theme-palenight","npx nuxi generate\n","bash","",[252,253,254],"code",{"__ignoreMap":250},[255,256,259,263,267],"span",{"class":257,"line":258},"line",1,[255,260,262],{"class":261},"sBMFI","npx",[255,264,266],{"class":265},"sfazB"," nuxi",[255,268,269],{"class":265}," generate\n",[271,272,274],"tip",{"icon":273},"i-lucide-check",[231,275,276,277,280],{},"此命令将创建一个包含您的静态站点的 ",[252,278,279],{},"dist/"," 目录。您可以将其上传到任何静态托管服务。",[231,282,283,284,287],{},"Nuxt 将使用内部爬虫自动预渲染所有页面，您可以通过 ",[252,285,286],{},"nitro.prerender"," 选项自定义其行为。",[289,290,292],"note",{"to":291},"https://nuxt.com/docs/getting-started/prerendering",[231,293,294],{},"了解更多关于 Nuxt 预渲染的信息。",[226,296,298],{"id":297},"数据库怎么办","数据库怎么办？",[231,300,301,302,307],{},"Nuxt Content 将使用 ",[303,304,306],"a",{"href":305},"/docs/advanced/database#wasm-sqlite-in-browser","WASM SQLite"," 在浏览器中加载数据库，这样，内容查询发生在客户端导航或操作时时，会在浏览器中运行。",[309,310,311],"style",{},"html pre.shiki code .sBMFI, html code.shiki .sBMFI{--shiki-light:#E2931D;--shiki-default:#FFCB6B;--shiki-dark:#FFCB6B}html pre.shiki code .sfazB, html code.shiki .sfazB{--shiki-light:#91B859;--shiki-default:#C3E88D;--shiki-dark:#C3E88D}html .light .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-light);background: var(--shiki-light-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-light-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-light-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-light-text-decoration);}html.light .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-light);background: var(--shiki-light-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-light-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-light-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-light-text-decoration);}html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .dark .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-dark);background: var(--shiki-dark-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-dark-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-dark-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-dark-text-decoration);}html.dark .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-dark);background: var(--shiki-dark-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-dark-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-dark-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-dark-text-decoration);}",{"title":250,"searchDepth":313,"depth":313,"links":314},2,[315,316,317],{"id":228,"depth":313,"text":229},{"id":239,"depth":313,"text":240},{"id":297,"depth":313,"text":298},"如何使用静态站点生成将 Nuxt Content 部署到静态托管。","md",null,{},{"title":116},{"title":221,"description":318},"uwh6Vdu1dYsaPAbsLA0vRu13geZ44r43EnQi8kWqSPA",[326,328],{"title":112,"path":113,"stem":114,"description":327,"children":-1},"Node 预设是 Nuxt 和 Nuxt Content 的默认预设。它用于在 Node.js 上构建和运行 Nuxt 应用程序。",{"title":120,"path":121,"stem":122,"description":329,"children":-1},"如何在各种无服务器平台上部署 Nuxt Content。",1751727802716]